Insider Activity


Individual




Allan P. Merrill



Mr. Allan P. Merrill is President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Beazer Homes USA, Inc., a Member at Homebuilding Community Foundation, President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Beazer Homes Corp., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Beazer Homes Texas Holdings, Inc., and President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Beazer Homes Holdings Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Beazer Homes USA, Inc., Builder Homesite, Inc., Beazer Homes Corp., Beazer Homes Texas Holdings, Inc., and Beazer Homes Holdings Corp.
Mr. Merrill was previously employed as EVP-Strategy & Corporate Development by InfoTouch Corp, President by Homebuilder.com, and a Managing Director by UBS AG.
He received his undergraduate degree from The Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania.



