Alan Merrill

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Allan P Sachs)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Alan Merrill



Merrill in 2013



Background information


Birth name
Allan Preston Sachs


Born
(1951-02-19) February 19, 1951 (age 66)
The Bronx, New York, United States


Genres
Glam rock, pop


Occupation(s)
